estions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I would feel guilty or ashamed of myself I did not do it]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I know I can earn rewards for doing it]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I personally believe it is the best thing for my health ]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because others would be upset with me if I did not do it]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I want to earn as much rewards as possible]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I have carefully thought about it and believe being physically active is very important for many aspects of my life ]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I would feel bad about myself if I did not do it	]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I would be angry at myself if I did not get the rewards]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because being physically active is an important choice I really want to make ]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I feel pressure from others to do this]; You are almost done. This is the final page with questions.     We want to know what drives you to be more physically active. Below you will find statements related to achieving your goals. To what extent do you agree with the following statements?      I want to be more physically active because….  [Because I feel pressure from the rewards to do this]